OL,3,CMeet Torsten Bell, the new MP for
OL,4,CSwansea West
OL,6,FTorsten Bell likes it strong.
OL,8,F"There's nothing worse than insipid
OL,9,Ftea" he tells me while making us a
OL,10,Fcuppa in his kitchen. "The bag must
OL,11,Fnot be removed."
OL,13,FWe also had a good discussion on the
OL,14,Fmerits of air fryers. They play a
OL,15,Fbigger role in Torsten's life right
OL,16,Fnow than you might think.
OL,18,FHis latest book, Great Britain? How We
OL,19,FGet Our Future Back is competing
OL,20,Fagainst the latest air fryer cookbook
OL,21,Ffor public attention.
