OL,3,CMeet Torsten Bell, the new MP for
OL,4,CSwansea West
OL,6,FAny publisher will tell you, it's the
OL,7,Ffryer that wins. I figure this is the
OL,8,Fnot the kind of conversation the new
OL,9,FSwansea West MP is used to having.
OL,11,FMaybe his old bosses, like former
OL,12,FChancellor Alistair Darling or Ed
OL,13,FMiliband, had strong views on airfryed
OL,14,Fsalmon skewers, but I somehow doubt it.
OL,16,FTorsten is a thinker, or to use a
OL,17,FWestminster term a, "policy wonk."
OL,18,FUntil recently he was head of the
OL,19,FResolution Foundation think tank.
