OL,3,CMeet Torsten Bell, the new MP for
OL,4,CSwansea West
OL,6,FHe's been Labour's Director of Policy
OL,7,Fand how he's an MP, finding his way
OL,8,Faround Uplands and Hafod in his new
OL,9,Fconstituency.
OL,11,F"You're used to talking about economic
OL,12,Fpolicy" I say, "but what about dealing
OL,13,Fwith potholes and dog fouling?"
OL,15,FHe jumps on the chance to explain why
OL,16,Fpotholes are important: "Politics is
OL,17,Fabout delivering for people, and
OL,18,Fpotholes, which people might joke
OL,19,Fabout, are real things."
