OL,3,CMeet Torsten Bell, the new MP for
OL,4,CSwansea West
OL,6,FThis year, in its annual Left
OL,7,FPowerlist the Newstatesman put him at
OL,8,Fnumber 9, beating Tony Blair (12), his
OL,9,Fold boss Ed Miliband (15) and the
OL,10,FArchbishop of Canterbury (27).
OL,12,FHe's not even in the cabinet - but
OL,13,Fhe's tipped to be, one day. So, what's
OL,14,Fit like having people say such things
OL,15,Fabout you?
OL,17,F"Well it's nicer than people saying
OL,18,Fthis person is useless" he says.
